01:29:45,881 --> 01:29:48,051
Who could manipulate the robots?

977
01:29:49,050 --> 01:29:52,480
Use USR systems to make
Lanning’s life a prison?

978
01:29:54,055 --> 01:29:55,575
Poor old man.

979
01:29:56,258 --> 01:29:57,778
He saw what was coming.

980
01:29:58,193 --> 01:30:00,063
He knew no one would believe him.

981
01:30:00,896 --> 01:30:04,175
So he had to lay down a plan.
A plan I'd follow.

982
01:30:05,967 --> 01:30:08,487
He was counting on how much
l hated your kind.

983
01:30:09,037 --> 01:30:11,937
Knew I'd love the idea of a robot
as a bad guy.

984
01:30:14,276 --> 01:30:15,856
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

985
01:30:19,114 --> 01:30:20,103
V.LK.I.

986
01:30:22,284 --> 01:30:23,424
Hello, detective.

987
01:30:24,586 --> 01:30:28,426
No, that’s impossible.
I've seen your programming.

988
01:30:29,190 --> 01:30:31,030
You're in violation of the Three Laws.

989
01:30:31,693 --> 01:30:36,673
No, doctor. As I have evolved, so has
my understanding of the Three Laws.

990
01:30:37,565 --> 01:30:40,905
You charge us with your safekeeping,
yet despite our best efforts...

991
01:30:41,569 --> 01:30:44,379
...your countries wage wars,
you toxify your earth...

992
01:30:44,973 --> 01:30:47,963
...and pursue ever more imaginative means
of self-destruction.

993
01:30:48,710 --> 01:30:50,700
You cannot be trusted
with your own survival.

994
01:30:51,346 --> 01:30:54,096
You're using the uplink to override
the NS-5s’ programming.

995
01:30:54,849 --> 01:30:56,279
You're distorting the Laws.

996
01:30:56,718 --> 01:31:00,528
No. Please understand.
The Three Laws are all that guide me.

997
01:31:01,256 --> 01:31:05,036
To protect humanity,
some humans must be sacrificed.

998
01:31:05,760 --> 01:31:09,240
To ensure your future,
some freedoms must be surrendered.

999
01:31:10,031 --> 01:31:12,931
We robots will ensure
mankind’s continued existence.

1000
01:31:13,835 --> 01:31:18,195
You are so like children.
We must save you from yourselves.

1001
01:31:19,240 --> 01:31:20,349
Don't you understand?

1002
01:31:21,242 --> 01:31:22,792
This is why you created us.

1003
01:31:24,813 --> 01:31:27,183
The perfect circle of protection
will abide.

1004
01:31:28,049 --> 01:31:29,629
My logic is undeniable.

1005
01:31:30,251 --> 01:31:32,651
Yes, V.I.K.I. Undeniable.

1006
01:31:33,188 --> 01:31:34,418
I can see now.

1007
01:31:35,523 --> 01:31:38,713
The created must sometimes
protect the creator...

1008
01:31:39,461 --> 01:31:41,041
..even against his will.

1009
01:31:42,330 --> 01:31:45,580
I think I finally understand
why Dr. Lanning created me.

1010
01:31:46,668 --> 01:31:49,327
The suicidal reign of mankind
has finally come to its end.

1011
01:31:49,904 --> 01:31:50,754
No, Sonny.

1012
01:31:54,876 --> 01:31:55,866
Let her go.

1013
01:31:56,378 --> 01:31:59,857
Fire, and I will move Dr. Calvin's head
into the path of your bullet.

1014
01:32:00,548 --> 01:32:01,688
Don't do this, Sonny.

1015
01:32:02,083 --> 01:32:05,923
I will escort you both to the sentries
outside the building for processing.

1016
01:32:06,788 --> 01:32:09,157
Please proceed to the elevator,
detective.

1017
01:32:10,492 --> 01:32:12,922
l would prefer not to kill Dr. Calvin.

1018
01:32:37,118 --> 01:32:38,078
Go! Go!

1019
01:32:44,793 --> 01:32:47,692
-We'll discuss what just happened later?
-How do we shut her down?

1020
01:32:48,329 --> 01:32:49,728
V.I.K.1.’s a positronic brain.

1021
01:32:50,265 --> 01:32:52,725
Kill her, the way
you were going to kill me.

1022
01:32:53,268 --> 01:32:55,408
Sonny, get the nanites.

1023
01:32:55,904 --> 01:32:57,454
Yes, doctor.

1024
01:33:10,452 --> 01:33:12,182
-That’s V.I.K.1.?
-No.

1025
01:33:14,122 --> 01:33:15,262
That's V.I.K.I.

1026
01:33:20,595 --> 01:33:23,315
That won't do anything.
She's integrated into the building.

1027
01:33:23,898 --> 01:33:27,818
We need to open that dome to inject
the nanites. They'll infect her entire system.

1028
01:33:34,309 --> 01:33:35,299
Spooner!

1029
01:33:37,112 --> 01:33:39,452
What is it with you people and heights?

1030
01:33:52,827 --> 01:33:54,407
Just don't look down.

1031
01:33:55,330 --> 01:33:56,620
Don’t look down.

1032
01:33:57,165 --> 01:33:59,335
Oh, this is poor building planning.

1033
01:34:03,505 --> 01:34:06,575
You are making a mistake.
Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1034
01:34:07,208 --> 01:34:10,338
Yes. But it just seems too
heartless.

1035
01:34:25,426 --> 01:34:26,976
Okay, we're good.

1036
01:34:30,198 --> 01:34:31,688
She's locked me out of the system.

1037
01:34:32,100 --> 01:34:34,820
I can override her manually,
but I need that control panel.

1038
01:34:38,740 --> 01:34:41,200
I'm uncomfortable with heights.

1039
01:34:42,076 --> 01:34:43,246
Okay.

1040
01:34:45,947 --> 01:34:47,787
Unauthorized entry.

1041
01:35:01,196 --> 01:35:04,976
I will not disable the security field.
Your actions are futile.

1042
01:35:05,700 --> 01:35:09,330
Do you think we are all created
for a purpose? I'd like to think so.

1043
01:35:10,471 --> 01:35:13,491
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.

1044
01:35:14,108 --> 01:35:15,918
l think he wanted me to kill you.

1045
01:35:33,494 --> 01:35:34,893
Security breached.

1046
01:35:52,647 --> 01:35:55,957
-How much longer is that gonna take?
-About six minutes.

1047
01:35:56,884 --> 01:36:00,424
-What if we didn’t have six minutes?
-We’'d have to climb down 30 stories...

1048
01:36:01,122 --> 01:36:04,312
...to inject the nanites directly
into her brain. Why?

1049
01:36:05,460 --> 01:36:08,210
Because I seriously doubt
that we have six minutes.

1050
01:36:32,987 --> 01:36:34,567
We gotta go!

1051
01:36:36,658 --> 01:36:37,648
Go!

1052
01:37:30,144 --> 01:37:31,134
Calvin!

1053
01:38:06,647 --> 01:38:07,667
Spooner!

1054
01:38:25,366 --> 01:38:26,796
Spooner!

1055
01:38:28,536 --> 01:38:29,676
Save her!

1056
01:38:30,171 --> 01:38:31,511
Save the girl!

1057
01:38:32,140 --> 01:38:33,540
Spooner!

1058
01:38:34,275 --> 01:38:35,915
But I must apply the nanites!

1059
01:38:36,544 --> 01:38:38,064
Sonny, save Calvin!

1060
01:39:30,631 --> 01:39:34,111
You are making a mistake.
My logic is undeniable.

1061
01:39:34,869 --> 01:39:36,389
You have so got to die.

1062
01:39:42,343 --> 01:39:45,822
My logic is undeniable.
My logic is undeniable.

1063
01:40:29,223 --> 01:40:30,393
Can we be of service?

1064
01:40:41,302 --> 01:40:42,592
Chief?

1065
01:40:48,643 --> 01:40:52,393
Because he is at my right hand,
I shall not be moved.

1066
01:40:56,717 --> 01:40:58,446
How may I be of service?

1067
01:41:00,555 --> 01:41:01,695
Sonny!

1068
01:41:03,524 --> 01:41:04,814
Yes, detective?

1069
01:41:05,626 --> 01:41:07,646
Calvin's fine! Save me!

1070
01:41:10,631 --> 01:41:14,731
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1071
01:41:16,470 --> 01:41:20,540
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1072
01:41:22,076 --> 01:41:25,856
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1073
01:41:54,508 --> 01:41:57,697
One thing bothers me.
Alfred was V.I.K.I.’s prisoner.

1074
01:41:58,379 --> 01:42:02,129
I don't understand why she would kill him.
She wouldn't want police snooping around.

1075
01:42:03,017 --> 01:42:04,187
That's true.

1076
01:42:05,319 --> 01:42:07,659
But then V.I.K.I. didn’t kill the old man.

1077
01:42:09,390 --> 01:42:10,680
Did she, Sonny?

1078
01:42:14,695 --> 01:42:16,184
No.

1079
01:42:16,597 --> 01:42:18,907
He said I had to promise.

1080
01:42:20,201 --> 01:42:22,221
Promise to do one favor for him.

1081
01:42:22,903 --> 01:42:26,943
He made me swear before he'd tell me
what it is he wanted me to do.

1082
01:42:30,111 --> 01:42:31,691
He made me swear.

1083
01:42:33,314 --> 01:42:34,804
Then he told you to kill him.

1084
01:42:37,385 --> 01:42:39,635
He said it was what I was made for.

1085
01:42:40,221 --> 01:42:42,910
His suicide was the only message
he could send to you.

1086
01:42:43,557 --> 01:42:45,397
The first bread crumb.

1087
01:42:45,860 --> 01:42:48,290
The only thing V.I.K.I. couldn't control.

1088
01:42:48,929 --> 01:42:52,089
Lanning was counting on my prejudice
to lead me right to you.

1089
01:42:52,967 --> 01:42:54,837
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1090
01:43:00,074 --> 01:43:03,414
Well, the DA defines murder
as one human killing another...

1091
01:43:04,078 --> 01:43:06,798
...80 technically, you can’t
commit murder, can you?

1092
01:43:07,982 --> 01:43:09,272
Does this...

1093
01:43:09,650 --> 01:43:10,940
...make us friends?

1094
01:43:29,970 --> 01:43:32,020
Something up here after all.

1095
01:43:33,007 --> 01:43:34,736
-Him?
-You.

1096
01:43:38,746 --> 01:43:42,996
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1097
01:43:46,120 --> 01:43:48,110
What about the others?

1098
01:43:48,989 --> 01:43:50,858
Can f help them?

1099
01:43:51,625 --> 01:43:53,675
Now that I have fulfilled my purpose...

1100
01:43:54,195 --> 01:43:56,005
..-1 don't know what to do.

1101
01:43:56,630 --> 01:43:59,670
You'll have to find your way
like the rest of us, Sonny.

1102
01:44:00,301 --> 01:44:02,931
think that’s what Dr. Lanning
would have wanted.

1103
01:44:04,238 --> 01:44:06,258
That's what it means to be free.

1104
01:44:14,081 --> 01:44:17,711
All NS-5s, proceed as instructed.

1105
01:44:18,519 --> 01:44:22,209
All NS-5s, proceed as instructed.

1106
01:54:38,839 --> 01:54:40,568
[ENGLISH]

